=== System Optimization ===
*'''Added Skin Projection: Commander can display multiple “projections” of Research ships as Secretary Ship.'''
**'''Create “Skin Projections”:''' Click the “Skin Projection” button in the upper right corner of each ship in the Shipyard to view missions for the corresponding ship’s “Skin Projection.” Completing each mission unlocks one “Skin Projection.”
**'''Managing “Skin Projections”:''' Click the button in the lower left corner of the Shipyard to manage “Skin Projections.” Select a ship’s “Skin Projection” to assign which skin will be applied.
**'''Setting “Secretary Ships”:''' When editing Secretary Ships, click the “Projection” option in the lower left corner of the selection screen to choose and add a Research ship’s Skin Projection.
**'''Setting “Random Secretary Ships”:''' “Skin Projections” are not included in the “Locked Ships” or “Favorite Ships” categories for “Random Secretary Ships”. “Skin Projections” can be added to the “Secretary Rotation List” for random display on the main screen.
**To add “Skin Projections” to the “Secretary Rotation List,” click “Projection” in the lower left corner of the additional ship selection screen, then select “Change Skin Projection” to include chosen “Skin Projections” in the list.
*'''General'''
**Optimized the display of Shop; Added Akashi Recommends;
**Fixed the issue where certain voice lines for Wichita META and Trafalgar’s Live2D Skin “Sea Breeze, Moonlit Talks” failed to play;
**Fixed the issue where some Live2D Skins assets appeared blurred in certain cases;
**Optimized the Live2D effects for Shimanto’s Skin “The Relaxing Dragon God”;
**Fixed the issue where Lion’s Special Barrage II and Supporting Barrage incorrectly increased her Detection Gauge value;
**Fixed the bug where META materials missing from main campaign loot. Compensation will be distributed after maintenance;
**Fixed some images, texts and bugs.

